### Extract fields from a document
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/extract
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "document_type": "invoice",
    "document_ids": ["{{document_id}}"],
    "case_type": "generic"
}

### Extract specific fields only
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/extract
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "document_type": "invoice",
    "document_ids": ["{{document_id}}"],
    "case_type": "generic",
    "fields": ["total_amount", "invoice_date"]
}

### Extract in direct mode (no references)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/extract
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "document_type": "invoice",
    "document_ids": ["{{document_id}}"],
    "extraction_mode": "direct",
    "reference_granularity": "none"
}

### Extract with page-level references
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/extract
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "document_type": "invoice",
    "document_ids": ["{{document_id}}"],
    "reference_granularity": "page",
    "content_mode": "markdown"
}

### Extract from specific pages
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/extract
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "document_type": "invoice",
    "document_ids": ["{{document_id}}"],
    "page_ids": ["{{page_id}}"]
}

### Extract with reference inference
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/extract
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "document_type": "invoice",
    "document_ids": ["{{document_id}}"],
    "infer_references": true
}

### Get stored field results for a document
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/field-results?document_id={{document_id}}

### Split and classify a multi-document file
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/split-classify
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "document_type": "generic",
    "document_ids": ["{{document_id}}"],
    "case_type": "generic"
}